column2: SELECT   p.ObjID, p.ra, p.dec, h.Photoz, f.rms  s.z, p.modelMag_g FROM  PhotoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID=p.objID JOIN FIRST f ON f.objID=p.objID JOIN Photoz h ON h.objID=p.objID WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.z between # and # AND  p.modelMag_g > # AND  f.rms BETWEEN # AND #
